cat << EOF
The PEAR::HTML_Crypt provides methods to encrypt
text, which
can be later be decrypted using JavaScript on
the client side

This is very useful to prevent spam robots
collecting email
addresses from your site, included is a
method to add mailto
links to the text being generated
